1167
01:20:55,440 --> 01:20:57,829
prescribed for his mother's
heroin addiction.

1168
01:20:57,920 --> 01:20:59,751
Lorraine Dunbar is the daughter

1169
01:20:59,840 --> 01:21:02,354
of the late Bradford playwright,
Andrea Dunbar,

1170
01:21:02,440 --> 01:21:05,000
who became famous 20 years ago
for her film...

1171
01:21:05,080 --> 01:21:07,036
- It's not very flattering, is it?
