1172
01:21:07,120 --> 01:21:10,351
...about life on the downtrodden
Buttershaw Estate in Bradford.

1173
01:21:10,440 --> 01:21:12,670
Lorraine was just 11
when her mother died

1174
01:21:12,760 --> 01:21:14,716
from a suspected
brain haemorrhage

1175
01:21:14,800 --> 01:21:18,588
and her daughter had descended
into drugs by the age of 14.

1176
01:21:18,680 --> 01:21:21,558
