had totally failed as a parent

1177
01:21:21,640 --> 01:21:24,552
by omission rather than commission.

1178
01:21:24,640 --> 01:21:28,155
Today she was jailed for three years
and nine months for manslaughter

1179
01:21:28,240 --> 01:21:30,549
by gross neglect of her son Harris.

